<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<title>ạ̉w̉mr bạlḥyạẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉w̉mr bạlḥyạẗ llqlb ạlly mạt
 ḥty̱ ạldẖkryạt nsynạ wạsẖfynạ
 qạdr m ạlʿẓạm mn kwm ạlḥṭạm
 tkẖlq jysẖ lmjdk ạ̉nfkẖ rwḥk fynạ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉sẖrq ʿlynạ .. bạ̹ydk dạwynạ
 ạ̉str mạḍynạ .. fy dm ạlmjrwḥ
 sẖdd ạ̹ydynạ .. ạ̹rfʿ ʿynynạ
 wạlnṣrẗ lynạ .. bqwẗ ạlrwḥ
 2- ʿsẖnạ lrwḥnạ .. wzạdt jrwḥnạ
 rạjʿyn lk sạmḥnạ .. wf qlbk ạ̹qblnạ
 dạ ạlly fạt kfạyẗ .. ʿysẖnạh llnfạyẗ
 ạ̹ksẖf ạlkẖbạyạ .. qdsnạ wṭhrnạ
 3- rjạnạ fy ạ̹ydk .. wf qwẗ ṣlybk
 nạdynạ nyjy lk .. ʿ ạlmyẗ tmsẖynạ
 ntgẖyr lṣwrtk .. wnfrḥ fy qrbk
 wlw ywm ḍʿfnạ .. mn tạny tqwynạ</lyrics>
</song>